              <p class="text-muted text-sm">Identify the spiritual lessons and challenges you need to overcome in this lifetime.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="rounded-lg shadow-[0_4px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] backdrop-blur border-[#ffffff29] bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-4">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-heading mb-2">🛤️ Spiritual Path:</h4>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm">Discover the most effective spiritual practices and path for your karmic evolution.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-lg shadow-[0_4px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] backdrop-blur border-[#ffffff29] bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-6 text-center">📊 Karmic Analysis Chart</h4>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-gray-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-500/10 to-gray-500/5 border border-gray-500/20">
              <span class="font-semibold">Saturn (Karma Planet)</span>
              <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓ Balanced</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-purple-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500/10 to-purple-500/5 border border-purple-500/20">
              <span class="font-semibold">Rahu (Material Desires)</span>
              <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓ Controlled</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-indigo-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500/10 to-indigo-500/5 border border-indigo-500/20">
              <span class="font-semibold">Ketu (Spiritual Detachment)</span>
              <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓ Awakened</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/10 to-blue-500/5 border border-blue-500/20">
              <span class="font-semibold">Jupiter (Spiritual Guru)</span>
              <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓ Strong</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-primary rounded-lg text-white">
              <span class="font-bold">Karmic Evolution Score</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-xl">92/100</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits of Spiritual Guidance -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">💫 Benefits of Spiritual Guidance</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted">Why spiritual guidance is essential for inner transformation</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="rounded-lg shadow-[0_4px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] backdrop-blur border-[#ffffff29] bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white text-xl">🕉️</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">Find Your Purpose</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Discover your life's true purpose and align your actions with your spiritual calling.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-lg shadow-[0_4px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] backdrop-blur border-[#ffffff29] bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white text-xl">🧘</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">Inner Peace</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Achieve deep inner peace, emotional balance, and spiritual harmony through guided practices.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-lg shadow-[0_4px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] backdrop-blur border-[#ffffff29] bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white text-xl">🔄</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">Karmic Healing</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Understand and heal past life karma to accelerate your spiritual evolution.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-lg shadow-[0_4px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] backdrop-blur border-[#ffffff29] bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white text-xl">📚</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">Spiritual Wisdom</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Gain deep spiritual wisdom and understanding of cosmic truths and universal laws.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-lg shadow-[0_4px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] backdrop-blur border-[#ffffff29] bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white text-xl">🦋</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">Personal Transformation</h3>
